#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:5
msgid "Accounting and Invoicing"
msgstr "Računovodstvo in izdajanje računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing is a standalone app designed to create invoices, send them to "
"customers, and manage payments. It also handles flows involving vendor "
"bills. On the other hand, the Accounting app is a comprehensive accounting "
"solution that allows the same actions and includes additional features such "
"as standard financial reports, bank reconciliation, budgets, asset "
"management, and more."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Invoicing je samostojna aplikacija, zasnovana za ustvarjanje računov, "
"pošiljanje strankam in upravljanje plačil. Prav tako obravnava tokove, ki "
"vključujejo dobaviteljeve račune. Po drugi strani je aplikacija Accounting "
"celovita računovodska rešitev, ki omogoča enaka dejanja in vključuje dodatne "
"funkcije, kot so standardna finančna poročila, usklajevanje bančnih "
"izpiskov, proračuni, upravljanje sredstev in drugo."

