"Prepričajte se, da je vaš :guilabel:`Bančni račun` pravilno konfiguriran v "
"Odoo z vašo številko IBAN in BIC."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:30
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, "
"open your bank journal, then fill out the :guilabel:`Account Number` "
"and :guilabel:`Bank` under the :guilabel:`Bank Account Number` column."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`, odprete svoj bančni dnevnik in nato izpolnite "
":guilabel:`Številka računa` in :guilabel:`Banka` v stolpcu "
":guilabel:`Številka bančnega računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:None
msgid "Bank account number column in the bank journal"
msgstr "Stolpec številke bančnega računa v bančnem dnevniku"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:38
msgid "Issue invoices with EPC QR codes"
msgstr "Izdajajte račune z QR kodami EPC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:40
msgid ""
"EPC QR codes are added automatically to your invoices. Customers whose bank "
"supports making payments via EPC QR codes will be able to scan the code and "
"pay the invoice."
msgstr ""
"QR kode EPC so samodejno dodane vašim računom. Stranke, katerih banka "
"podpira plačila prek QR kod EPC, bodo lahko skenirale kodo in plačale račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:43
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`, and create a "
"new invoice."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Računi` in "
"ustvarite nov račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:45
msgid ""
"Before posting it, open the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab. Odoo automatically "
"fills out the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` field with your IBAN."
msgstr ""
"Preden ga objavite, odprite zavihek :guilabel:`Druge informacije`. Odoo "
"samodejno izpolni polje :guilabel:`Banka prejemnika` z vašo številko IBAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:49
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, the account indicated in "
"the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` field is used to receive your customer's "
"payment. Odoo automatically populates this field with your IBAN by default "
"and uses it to generate the EPC QR code."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Druge informacije` se račun, naveden v polju "
":guilabel:`Banka prejemnika`, uporablja za prejemanje plačila stranke. Odoo "
"privzeto samodejno izpolni to polje z vašo številko IBAN in jo uporabi za "
"ustvarjanje QR kode EPC."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:53
msgid ""
"When the invoice is printed or previewed, the QR code is included at the "
"bottom."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun natisnjen ali prikazan v predogledu, je QR koda vključena na dnu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:None
msgid "QR code on a customer invoice"
msgstr "QR koda na računu stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/epc_qr_code.rst:59
msgid ""
"If you want to issue an invoice without an EPC QR code, remove the IBAN "
"indicated in the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` field, under "
"the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab of the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izdati račun brez QR kode EPC, odstranite številko IBAN, navedeno "
"v polju :guilabel:`Banka prejemnika`, v zavihku :guilabel:`Druge "
"informacije` računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:3
msgid "Incoterms"
msgstr "Incoterms"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:5
msgid ""
":abbr:`Incoterms (International Commercial Terms)` are standardized trade "
"terms used in international transactions to define the rights and "
"responsibilities of buyers and sellers. They establish the obligations "
"related to the delivery of goods, the transfer of risks, and the "
"distribution of costs between the parties involved. Incoterms specify "
"important details, such as the point at which the risk and costs transfer "
"from the seller to the buyer, the responsibility for transportation, "
"insurance, customs clearance, and other relevant aspects of the transaction."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`Incoterms (Mednarodni blagovni pogoji)` so standardizirani trgovinski "
"pogoji, ki se uporabljajo v mednarodnih transakcijah za opredelitev pravic "
"in obveznosti kupcev in prodajalcev. Določajo obveznosti v zvezi z dostavo "
"blaga, prenosom tveganj in porazdelitvijo stroškov med vpletenimi stranmi. "
"Incoterms določajo pomembne podrobnosti, kot so točka, v kateri se tveganje "
"in stroški prenesejo s prodajalca na kupca, odgovornost za prevoz, "
"zavarovanje, carinjenje in druge relevantne vidike transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:13
msgid "By default, all 11 Incoterms are available in Odoo:"
msgstr "Privzeto je v Odoo na voljo vseh 11 incotermsov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:15
msgid "**EXW**: Ex works"
msgstr "**EXW**: Franco tovarna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:16
msgid "**FCA**: Free carrier"
msgstr "**FCA**: Prosto prevozniku"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:17
msgid "**FAS**: Free alongside ship"
msgstr "**FAS**: Prosto ob ladji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:18
msgid "**FOB**: Free on board"
msgstr "**FOB**: Prosto na krovu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:19
msgid "**CFR**: Cost and freight"
msgstr "**CFR**: Stroški in vozarina"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:20
msgid "**CIF**: Cost, insurance and freight"
msgstr "**CIF**: Stroški, zavarovanje in vozarina"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:21
msgid "**CPT**: Carriage paid to"
msgstr "**CPT**: Vozarina plačana do"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:22
msgid "**CIP**: Carriage and insurance paid to"
msgstr "**CIP**: Vozarina in zavarovanje plačana do"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:23
msgid "**DPU**: Delivered at place unloaded"
msgstr "**DPU**: Dostavljeno na kraj raztovorjeno"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:24
msgid "**DAP**: Delivered at place"
msgstr "**DAP**: Dostavljeno na kraj"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms.rst:25
msgid "**DDP**: Delivered duty paid"
msgstr "**DDP**: Dostavljeno z opravljeno carinsko obveznostjo"

