"remaining balance is identified if the total debits and credits do not match "
"when records are compared with bank transactions. This balance must either "
"be reconciled later or written off immediately."
msgstr ""
"Med postopkom :doc:`usklajevanja z banko <bank/reconciliation>` je "
"ugotovljeno preostalo stanje, če se skupni debeti in krediti ne ujemajo pri "
"primerjavi zapisov z bančnimi transakcijami. To stanje je treba bodisi "
"uskladiti kasneje bodisi takoj odpisati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:82
msgid "For a single invoice or bill"
msgstr "Za posamezen račun ali predračun"

