#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:148
msgid "|sdd| rejections"
msgstr "Zavrnitve |sdd|"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:150
msgid ""
"|sdd| rejections can occur for several reasons, the most common being "
"insufficient funds in the customer's account. With |sdd|, the recipient's "
"account is credited before the funds are actually debited from the "
"customer's account. As a result, if an |sdd| payment is later rejected, the "
"bank automatically withdraws the amount of that payment from the recipient's "
"account, and a new transaction for a negative amount is created to reflect "
"the |sdd| rejection."
msgstr ""
"Do zavrnitev |sdd| lahko pride iz več razlogov, najpogostejši je pomanjkanje "
"sredstev na strankinemu računu. Pri |sdd| je prejemnikov račun pripisan, "
"preden so sredstva dejansko odpisana s strankinega računa. Posledično, če je "
"plačilo |sdd| pozneje zavrnjeno, banka samodejno umakne znesek tega plačila "
"s prejemnikovega računa in ustvari novo transakcijo za negativni znesek, ki "
"odraža zavrnitev |sdd|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:156
msgid ""
"In this case, you must reverse the journal entry associated with the "
"rejected payment and reconcile the reversal of the journal entry with the "
"transaction for the |sdd| rejection. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:160
msgid "Access the invoice linked to the rejected |sdd| payment."
msgstr "Dostopajte do računa, povezanega z zavrnjenim plačilom |sdd|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:161
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(information)` icon in the "
"footer of the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab, then click :guilabel:`View` to "
"access the payment associated with the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(informacije)` v nogi "
"zavihka :guilabel:`Postavke računa`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Prikaži`, da "
"dostopate do plačila, povezanega z računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:164
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Journal entry` smart button to access the related "
"journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite pametno tipko :guilabel:`Vnos v dnevnik`, da dostopate do "
"povezanega vnosa v dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:165
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Reverse entry`, optionally edit the fields in the popup, "
"then click :guilabel:`Reverse`. A reversal entry is created with "
"a :guilabel:`Reference` mentioning the initial journal entry. As a result, "
"the invoice is marked as :guilabel:`Not paid`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Storniraj vnos`, po želji uredite polja v pojavnem oknu, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Storniraj`. Ustvari se stornirani vnos z "
":guilabel:`Referenco`, ki omenja prvotni vnos v dnevnik. Posledično je račun "
"označen kot :guilabel:`Neplačan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:168
msgid ""
":ref:`Access the bank journal's reconciliation view <accounting/"
"reconciliation/access>` and :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` the transaction created for the |sdd| rejection with the "
"reversal of the entry related to the payment."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dostopajte do pogleda uskladitve bančnega dnevnika <accounting/"
