"preceding taxes` will be based on a modified sales price of $1100."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:415
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Included in Price` is enabled, subsequent taxes "
"with :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` will be based on a "
"modified sales price equal to the original sales price minus the tax amount."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:420
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1100, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax with :guilabel:`Included in Price` "
"and :guilabel:`Affect base of subsequent taxes`. Any subsequent tax "
"with :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` will be based on a "
"modified sales price of $1000."
