#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:218
msgid "Odoo AvaTax settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve Odoo AvaTax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:220
msgid ""
"To integrate the *AvaTax* :abbr:`API (application programming interface)` "
"with Odoo, go to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` section. The :guilabel:`AvaTax` fields in the :guilabel:`Taxes` "
"section is where the *AvaTax* configurations are made, and the credentials "
"are entered in."
msgstr ""
"Za integracijo :abbr:`API-ja (vmesnika za programiranje aplikacij)` *AvaTax* "
"z Odoo pojdite v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`. Polja :guilabel:`AvaTax` v razdelku :guilabel:`Davki` so mesto, "
"kjer se opravijo konfiguracije *AvaTax* in vnesejo poverilnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:225
msgid ""
"First, tick the checkbox to the left of the :guilabel:`AvaTax` settings, to "
"activate *AvaTax* on the database. This is a quick, convenient way to "
"activate and deactivate *AvaTax* tax calculation on the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Najprej označite potrditveno polje levo od nastavitev :guilabel:`AvaTax`, da "
"aktivirate *AvaTax* v podatkovni bazi. To je hiter in priročen način za "
"aktiviranje in deaktiviranje izračuna davkov *AvaTax* v podatkovni bazi Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:None
msgid "Configure AvaTax settings"
msgstr "Konfiguracija nastavitev AvaTax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:236
msgid ""
"First, select the :guilabel:`Environment` in which the company wishes to use "
"*AvaTax* in. It can either be :guilabel:`Sandbox` or :guilabel:`Production`."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite :guilabel:`Okolje`, v katerem želi podjetje uporabljati "
"*AvaTax*. Lahko je :guilabel:`Peskovnik` ali :guilabel:`Produkcija`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:240
msgid ""
"For help determining which *AvaTax* environment to use "
"(either :guilabel:`Production` or :guilabel:`Sandbox`), visit: `Sandbox vs "
"Production environments <https://knowledge.avalara.com/bundle/"
"fzc1692293626742/page/sandbox-vs-production.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za pomoč pri določanju, katero okolje *AvaTax* uporabiti "
"(:guilabel:`Produkcija` ali :guilabel:`Peskovnik`), obiščite: `Peskovnik "
"proti produkcijskemu okolju <https://knowledge.avalara.com/bundle/"
"fzc1692293626742/page/sandbox-vs-production.html>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:245
msgid "Credentials"
msgstr "Poverilnice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:247
msgid ""
"Now, the credentials can be entered in. The *AvaTax* :guilabel:`Account ID` "
"should be entered in the :guilabel:`API ID` field, and "
"the :guilabel:`License Key` should be entered in the :guilabel:`API Key` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko vnesete poverilnice. *AvaTax* :guilabel:`ID računa` je treba "
"vnesti v polje :guilabel:`ID API-ja`, :guilabel:`Licenčni ključ` pa v polje "
":guilabel:`Ključ API-ja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:252
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Account ID` can be found by logging into the *AvaTax* portal "
"(`sandbox <https://sandbox.admin.avalara.com/>`_ or `production <https://"
"admin.avalara.com/>`_). In the upper-right corner, click on the initials of "
"the user and :guilabel:`Account`. The :guilabel:`Account ID` is listed first."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID računa` najdete tako, da se prijavite v portal *AvaTax* "
"(`peskovnik <https://sandbox.admin.avalara.com/>`_ ali `produkcija <https://"
"admin.avalara.com/>`_). V zgornjem desnem kotu kliknite na inicialkah "
"uporabnika in :guilabel:`Račun`. :guilabel:`ID računa` je naveden na prvem "
"mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:257
msgid ""
"To access the :guilabel:`License Key` see this documentation: :ref:`avatax/"
"create_avalara_credentials`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:260
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Company Code` field, enter the Avalara company code for "
"the company being configured. Avalara interprets this as `DEFAULT`, if it is "
"not set. The :guilabel:`Company Code` can be accessed in the Avalara "
"management portal."
msgstr ""
"Za polje :guilabel:`Koda podjetja` vnesite kodo podjetja Avalara za "
"podjetje, ki se konfigurira. Avalara to interpretira kot `DEFAULT`, če ni "
"nastavljeno. :guilabel:`Kodo podjetja` lahko dostopate v upravljalnem "
"portalu Avalara."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:264
msgid ""
"First, log into the *AvaTax* portal (`sandbox <https://"
"sandbox.admin.avalara.com/>`_ or `production <https://admin.avalara.com/"
">`_). Then, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> Manage Companies`. "
"The :guilabel:`Company Code` value is located in the row of "
"the :guilabel:`Company` in the :guilabel:`Company Code` column."
msgstr ""
"Najprej se prijavite v portal *AvaTax* (`peskovnik <https://"
"sandbox.admin.avalara.com/>`_ ali `produkcija <https://admin.avalara.com/>`_)"
". Nato se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Upravljanje podjetij`. "
"Vrednost :guilabel:`Koda podjetja` se nahaja v vrstici :guilabel:`Podjetje` "
"v stolpcu :guilabel:`Koda podjetja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:None
msgid "AvaTax company code highlighted on the company details page."
msgstr "Koda podjetja AvaTax je poudarjena na strani s podrobnostmi podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:274
msgid "Transaction options"
msgstr "Možnosti transakcij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:276
msgid ""
"There are two transactional settings in the Odoo *AvaTax* settings that can "
"be configured: :guilabel:`Use UPC` and :guilabel:`Commit Transactions`."
msgstr ""
"V nastavitvah Odoo *AvaTax* sta dve transakcijski nastavitvi, ki ju je "
"mogoče konfigurirati: :guilabel:`Uporabi UPC` in :guilabel:`Potrdi "
"transakcije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:279
msgid ""
"If the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Use UPC` is ticked, the transactions will "
"use Universal Product Codes (UPC), instead of custom defined codes in "
"Avalara. Consult a certified public accountant (CPA) for specific guidance."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno potrditveno polje poleg :guilabel:`Uporabi UPC`, bodo "
"transakcije uporabljale univerzalne kode izdelkov (UPC) namesto kod, ki so "
"bile po meri določene v Avalara. Za specifična navodila se posvetujte s "
"pooblaščenim računovodjem (CPA)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:283
msgid ""
"Should the :guilabel:`Commit Transactions` checkbox be ticked, then, the "
"transactions in the Odoo database will be committed for reporting in "
"*AvaTax*."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Potrdi transakcije`, bodo "
"transakcije v zbirki podatkov Odoo potrjene za poročanje v *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:287
msgid "Address validation"
msgstr "Preverjanje naslova"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:289
msgid ""
"The *Address Validation* feature ensures that the most up-to-date address by "
"postal standards is set on a contact in Odoo. This is important to provide "
"accurate tax calculations for customers."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija *Preverjanje naslova* zagotavlja, da je na stiku v Odoo nastavljen "
"najbolj posodobljen naslov po poštnih standardih. To je pomembno za "
"zagotavljanje natančnih davčnih izračunov za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:293
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Address Validation` feature only works with partners/"
"customers in North America."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija :guilabel:`Preverjanje naslova` deluje samo s partnerji/strankami v "
"Severni Ameriki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:295
msgid ""
"Additionally, tick the checkbox next to the :guilabel:`Address validation` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega označite potrditveno polje poleg polja :guilabel:`Preverjanje "
"naslova`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:298
msgid ""
"For accurate tax calculations, it is best practice to enter a complete "
"address for the contacts saved in the database. However, *AvaTax* can still "
"function by implementing a best effort attempt using only "
"the :guilabel:`Country`, :guilabel:`State`, and :guilabel:`Zip code`. These "
"are the three minimum required fields."
msgstr ""
"Za natančne davčne izračune je najboljša praksa vnesti popoln naslov za "
"stike, shranjene v zbirki podatkov. Vendar pa *AvaTax* lahko še vedno deluje "
"z izvajanjem najboljšega možnega poskusa z uporabo samo :guilabel:`Država`, "
":guilabel:`Stanje` in :guilabel:`Poštna številka`. To so tri minimalno "
"zahtevana polja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:303
msgid ":guilabel:`Save` the settings to implement the configuration."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Shranite` nastavitve za implementacijo konfiguracije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:306
msgid ""
"Manually :guilabel:`Validate` the address by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Contacts app`, and selecting a contact. Now that the "
"*AvaTax* module has been configured on the database, a :guilabel:`Validate` "
"button appears directly below the :guilabel:`Address`."
msgstr ""
"Ročno :guilabel:`Preverite` naslov tako, da se pomaknete na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Stiki` in izberete stik. Sedaj, ko je modul "
"*AvaTax* konfiguriran v zbirki podatkov, se gumb :guilabel:`Preveri` prikaže "
"neposredno pod :guilabel:`Naslov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:310
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Validate`, and a pop-up window appears with "
"a :guilabel:`Validated Address` and :guilabel:`Original Address` listed. If "
"the :guilabel:`Validated Address` is the correct mailing address for tax "
"purposes, click :guilabel:`Save Validated`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Preveri` in prikaže se pojavno okno z "
":guilabel:`Preverjenim naslovom` in :guilabel:`Izvirnim naslovom`. Če je "
":guilabel:`Preverjeni naslov` pravilen poštni naslov za davčne namene, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani preverjeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:0
msgid ""
"Validate address pop-up window in Odoo with \"Save Validated\" button and "
"\"Validated\n"
"Address\" highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Pojavno okno za preverjanje naslova v Odoo z gumbom \"Shrani preverjeno\" in "
"\"Preverjenim\n"
"naslovom\" poudarjenim."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:320
msgid ""
"All previously-entered addresses for contacts in the Odoo database will need "
"to be validated using the manually validate process outlined above. "
"Addresses are not automatically validated if they were entered previously. "
"This only occurs upon tax calculation."
msgstr ""
"Vsi prej vneseni naslovi za stike v zbirki podatkov Odoo bo potrebno "
"preveriti z uporabo postopka ročnega preverjanja, opisanega zgoraj. Naslovi "
"niso samodejno preverjeni, če so bili vneseni prej. To se zgodi samo pri "
"davčnem izračunu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:325
msgid "Test connection"
msgstr "Preizkusi povezavo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:327
msgid ""
"After entering all the above information into the *AvaTax* setup on Odoo, "
"click :guilabel:`Test connection`. This ensures the :guilabel:`API ID` "
"and :guilabel:`API KEY` are correct, and a connection is made between Odoo "
"and the *AvaTax* application programming interface (API)."
msgstr ""
"Po vnosu vseh zgornjih informacij v nastavitev *AvaTax* v Odoo kliknite "
":guilabel:`Preizkusi povezavo`. To zagotavlja, da sta :guilabel:`API ID` in "
":guilabel:`API KEY` pravilna in da je vzpostavljena povezava med Odoo in "
"aplikacijskim programskim vmesnikom (API) *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:332
msgid "Sync parameters"
msgstr "Parametri sinhronizacije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:334
msgid ""
"Upon finishing the configuration and settings of the *AvaTax* section, click "
"the :guilabel:`Sync Parameters` button. This action synchronizes the "
"exemption codes from *AvaTax*."
msgstr ""
"Po zaključku konfiguracije in nastavitev razdelka *AvaTax* kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Sinhroniziraj parametre`. To dejanje sinhronizira kode oprostitev "
"iz *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:342
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> "
"Accounting: Fiscal Positions`. A :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` is listed "
"named, :guilabel:`Automatic Tax Mapping (AvaTax)`. Click it to open "
"*AvaTax's* fiscal position configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Nato se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Računovodstvo: Davčni položaji`. Naveden je :guilabel:`Davčni položaj` z "
"imenom :guilabel:`Samodejno preslikovanje davkov (AvaTax)`. Kliknite nanj, "
"da odprete konfiguracijo davčnega položaja *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:346
msgid "Here, ensure that the :guilabel:`Use AvaTax API` checkbox is ticked."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj se prepričajte, da je označeno potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Uporabi "
"AvaTax API`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:348
msgid ""
"Optionally, tick the checkbox next to the field labeled: :guilabel:`Detect "
"Automatically`. Should this option be ticked, then, Odoo will automatically "
"apply this :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` for transactions in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Izbirno označite potrditveno polje poleg polja z oznako :guilabel:`Samodejno "
"zaznaj`. Če je ta možnost označena, bo Odoo samodejno uporabil ta "
":guilabel:`Davčni položaj` za transakcije v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:352
msgid ""
"Enabling :guilabel:`Detect Automatically` also makes specific parameters, "
"such as :guilabel:`VAT required`, :guilabel:`Foreign Tax "
"ID`, :guilabel:`Country Group`, :guilabel:`Country`, :guilabel:`Federal "
"States`, or :guilabel:`Zip Range` appear. Filling these parameters filters "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` usage. Leaving them blank ensures all "
"calculations are made using this :guilabel:`Fiscal Position`."
msgstr ""
"Omogočanje možnosti :guilabel:`Samodejno zaznaj` povzroči tudi prikaz "
"določenih parametrov, kot so :guilabel:`Zahtevana DDV št.`, :guilabel:`Tuja "
"davčna številka`, :guilabel:`Skupina držav`, :guilabel:`Država`, "
":guilabel:`Zvezne države` ali :guilabel:`Obseg poštnih številk`. "
"Izpolnjevanje teh parametrov filtrira uporabo :guilabel:`Davčnega položaja`. "
"Če jih pustite prazne, se vsi izračuni izvajajo z uporabo tega "
":guilabel:`Davčnega položaja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:359
msgid ""
"Should the :guilabel:`Detect Automatically` checkbox not be ticked, each "
"customer will need to have the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` set on "
"their :guilabel:`Sales and Purchase` tab of the contact record. To do so, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Order --> Customers`, "
"or :menuselection:`Contacts app --> Contacts`. Then, select a customer or "
"contact to set the fiscal position on."
msgstr ""
"Če potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Samodejno zaznaj` ni označeno, bo treba za "
"vsakega stranko nastaviti :guilabel:`Davčni položaj` na zavihku "
":guilabel:`Prodaja in nabava` v zapisu kontakta. To storite tako, da se "
"pomaknete na :menuselection:`Prodaja --> Naročilo --> Stranke` ali "
":menuselection:`Kontakti --> Kontakti`. Nato izberite stranko ali kontakt, "
"na katerem želite nastaviti davčni položaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:365
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Sales and Purchase` tab, and down to the section "
"labeled, :guilabel:`Fiscal Position`. Set the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` "
"field to the fiscal position for the customer."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se na zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja in nabava` in navzdol do razdelka "
"z oznako :guilabel:`Davčni položaj`. Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Davčni "
"položaj` na davčni položaj za stranko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:370
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:431
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:39
msgid ":doc:`fiscal_positions`"
msgstr ":doc:`fiscal_positions`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:373
msgid "AvaTax accounts"
msgstr "AvaTax računi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:375
msgid ""
"Upon selecting the checkbox option for :guilabel:`Use AvaTax API` a "
"new :guilabel:`AvaTax` tab appears. Click into this tab to reveal two "
"different settings."
msgstr ""
"Po izbiri potrditvenega polja za :guilabel:`Uporabi AvaTax API` se prikaže "
"nov zavihek :guilabel:`AvaTax`. Kliknite na ta zavihek, da razkrijete dve "
"različni nastavitvi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:378
msgid ""
"The first setting is the :guilabel:`AvaTax Invoice Account`, while the "
"second is, :guilabel:`AvaTax Refund Account`. Ensure both accounts are set "
"for smooth end-of-year record keeping. Consult a certified public accountant "
"(CPA) for specific guidance on setting both accounts."
msgstr ""
"Prva nastavitev je :guilabel:`Račun za AvaTax račune`, druga pa "
":guilabel:`Račun za AvaTax povračila`. Prepričajte se, da sta oba računa "
"nastavljena za nemoteno vodenje evidenc ob koncu leta. Za specifična "
"navodila o nastavitvi obeh računov se posvetujte s pooblaščenim revizorjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:382
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` to implement the changes."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da uveljavite spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:385
msgid "Tax mapping"
msgstr "Preslikovanje davkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:387
msgid ""
"The *AvaTax* integration is available on sale orders and invoices with the "
"included *AvaTax* fiscal position."
msgstr ""
"Integracija *AvaTax* je na voljo za prodajna naročila in račune z vključenim "
"davčnim položajem *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:391
msgid ""
"Additionally, there is a :guilabel:`Tax Mapping` tab and :guilabel:`Account "
"Mapping` tab in the :guilabel:`Automatic Tax Mapping (AvaTax)` fiscal "
"position, where mapping for products can also be configured. To "
"access :guilabel:`Fiscal Positions` navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"app --> Configuration --> Accounting: Fiscal Positions`."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega sta v davčnem položaju :guilabel:`Samodejno preslikovanje davkov "
"(AvaTax)` zavihek :guilabel:`Preslikovanje davkov` in zavihek "
":guilabel:`Preslikovanje računov`, kjer je mogoče konfigurirati tudi "
"preslikovanje za izdelke. Za dostop do :guilabel:`Davčnih položajev` se "
"pomaknite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Računovodstvo: Davčni položaji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:397
msgid "Product category mapping"
msgstr "Preslikovanje kategorij izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:399
msgid ""
"Before using the integration, specify an :guilabel:`Avatax Category` on the "
"product categories. Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Product Categories`. Select the product category to add "
"the :guilabel:`AvaTax Category` to. In the :guilabel:`AvaTax Category` "
"field, select a category from the drop-down menu, or :guilabel:`Search "
"More...` to open the complete list of options."
msgstr ""
"Pred uporabo integracije določite :guilabel:`Kategorijo Avatax` na "
"kategorijah izdelkov. Pomaknite se na :menuselection:`Zaloga --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Kategorije izdelkov`. Izberite kategorijo izdelka, na "
"katero želite dodati :guilabel:`Kategorijo AvaTax`. V polju "
":guilabel:`Kategorija AvaTax` izberite kategorijo iz spustnega menija ali "
":guilabel:`Išči več...`, da odprete celoten seznam možnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:None
msgid "Specify AvaTax Category on products."
msgstr "Določite kategorijo AvaTax za izdelke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:410
msgid "Product mapping"
msgstr "Preslikovanje izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:412
msgid ""
"*AvaTax* Categories may be set on individual products, as well. To set "
"the :guilabel:`Avatax Category` navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --"
"> Products --> Products`. Select the product to add the :guilabel:`Avatax "
"Category` to. Under the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, on the far-"
"right, is a selector field labeled: :guilabel:`Avatax Category`. Finally, "
"click the drop-down menu, and select a category, or :guilabel:`Search "
"More...` to find one that is not listed."
msgstr ""
"Kategorije *AvaTax* je mogoče nastaviti tudi za posamezne izdelke. Za "
"nastavitev :guilabel:`Avatax Category` se pomaknite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Zaloga --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`. Izberite "
"izdelek, ki mu želite dodati :guilabel:`Avatax Category`. V zavihku "
":guilabel:`General Information`, na skrajni desni, je polje za izbiro z "
"oznako: :guilabel:`Avatax Category`. Nazadnje kliknite spustni meni in "
"izberite kategorijo ali :guilabel:`Search More...`, da poiščete kategorijo, "
"ki ni navedena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:419
msgid ""
"If both the product, and its category, have an :guilabel:`AvaTax Category` "
"set, the product's :guilabel:`AvaTax Category` takes precedence."
msgstr ""
"Če imata tako izdelek kot njegova kategorija nastavljeno :guilabel:`AvaTax "
"Category`, ima prednost :guilabel:`AvaTax Category` izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:None
msgid "Override product categories as needed."
msgstr "Po potrebi prepišite kategorije izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:427
msgid ""
"Mapping an :guilabel:`AvaTax Category` on either the *Product* or *Product "
"Category* should be completed for every *Product* or *Product Category*, "
"depending on the route that is chosen."
msgstr ""
"Preslikava :guilabel:`AvaTax Category` bodisi na *Izdelek* ali *Kategorijo "
"izdelka* mora biti izvedena za vsak *Izdelek* ali *Kategorijo izdelka*, "
"odvisno od izbrane poti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:432
msgid ":doc:`avatax/avatax_use`"
msgstr ":doc:`avatax/avatax_use`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:433
msgid ":doc:`avatax/avalara_portal`"
msgstr ":doc:`avatax/avalara_portal`"

