#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:160
msgid "Email expenses"
msgstr "Pošljite stroške po e-pošti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:162
msgid ""
"Instead of individually creating each expense in the **Expenses** app, "
"expenses can be automatically created by sending an email to an email alias."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da bi vsak strošek ustvarili ločeno v aplikaciji **Expenses**, se "
"lahko stroški ustvarijo samodejno s pošiljanjem e-pošte na e-poštni vzdevek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:165
msgid ""
"To do so, an email alias must first be configured. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Ensure the "
"checkbox beside :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` is ticked. The default email "
"alias is *expense@(domain).com*. Change the email alias by entering the "
"desired email in the field to the right of :guilabel:`Alias`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za to je treba najprej konfigurirati e-poštni vzdevek. Pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Prepričajte "
"se, da je potrditveno polje poleg :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` označeno. "
"Privzeti e-poštni vzdevek je *expense@(domain).com*. Spremenite e-poštni "
"vzdevek tako, da vnesete želeno e-pošto v polje na desni strani "
":guilabel:`Alias`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:None
msgid "Te default email that populates the expenses email alias."
msgstr ""

