msgstr ""
"Ko je vzdevek domene konfiguriran, je polje e-poštnega naslova vidno pod "
"funkcijo :guilabel:`Incoming Emails` na strani :guilabel:`Settings` v "
"aplikaciji **Expenses**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:189
msgid ""
"Once the email address has been entered, emails can be sent to that alias to "
"create new expenses, without having to be in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Ko je e-poštni naslov vnesen, lahko pošiljate e-pošto na ta vzdevek za "
