msgid ""
"To manage your existing own checks, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Vendors --> Own Checks`. This window shows critical information such as "
"the dates when checks need to be paid, the total quantity of checks, and the "
"total amount paid in checks."
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje obstoječih lastnih čekov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Lastni čeki`. To okno "
"prikazuje kritične informacije, kot so datumi, ko je treba čeke plačati, "
"skupno število čekov in skupni znesek, plačan s čeki."

