#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:401
msgid ""
"In the Chilean localization, the electronic invoice workflow includes "
"customer invoice issuance and vendor bill reception. The following diagram "
"explains how information is shared to the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)`, customers, and vendors."
msgstr ""
"V čilski lokalizaciji potek elektronskega računa vključuje izdajo računov "
"strankam in prejemanje računov dobaviteljev. Naslednja shema pojasnjuje, "
"kako se informacije delijo s :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, "
"strankami in dobavitelji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Diagram with Electronic invoice transactions."
msgstr "Shema s transakcijami elektronskega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:410
msgid "Customer invoice emission"
msgstr "Izdaja računa stranki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:412
msgid ""
"After the partners and journals are created and configured, the invoices are "
"created in the standard way. For Chile, one of the differences is the "
"document type that is automatically selected based on the taxpayer. The "
"document type can be changed manually if needed on the invoice by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so partnerji in dnevniki ustvarjeni in konfigurirani, se računi ustvarijo "
"na standardni način. Za Čile je ena od razlik vrsta dokumenta, ki je "
"samodejno izbrana glede na davčnega zavezanca. Vrsto dokumenta lahko po "
"potrebi ročno spremenite na računu tako, da se pomaknete na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Računi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Customer invoice document type selection."
msgstr "Izbira vrste dokumenta računa stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:422
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Documents type 33` electronic invoice must have at least one item "
"with tax, otherwise the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` rejects "
"the document validation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta 33` elektronski račun mora imeti vsaj eno "
"postavko z davkom, sicer :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` zavrne "
"preverjanje veljavnosti dokumenta."

