#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:346
msgid ""
"The account type is then flagged as :guilabel:`payable` "
"and :guilabel:`reconcilable` based on the account template."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta konta je nato označena kot :guilabel:`plačljivo` in "
":guilabel:`uskladljivo` na podlagi predloge konta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:354
msgid ""
"Journals are checked against the existing ones in Odoo to avoid duplicates, "
"even when importing multiple FEC files."
msgstr ""
"Dnevniki se preverjajo glede na obstoječe v Odoo, da se preprečijo "
"podvojitve, tudi pri uvozu več datotek FEC."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:357
msgid ""
"If a journal with the same code already exists, the existing journal is used "
"instead of creating a new one."
msgstr ""
"Če dnevnik z isto kodo že obstaja, se uporabi obstoječi dnevnik namesto "
"ustvarjanja novega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:360
msgid ""
"New journals have the prefix :guilabel:`FEC-` added to their name. For "
"example, :guilabel:`ACHATS` becomes :guilabel:`FEC-ACHATS`."
msgstr ""
"Novi dnevniki imajo predpono :guilabel:`FEC-`, dodano imenu. Na primer, "
":guilabel:`ACHATS` postane :guilabel:`FEC-ACHATS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:364
msgid ""
"Journals are *not* archived, allowing the user to manage them as desired."
msgstr ""
"Dnevniki *niso* arhivirani, kar uporabniku omogoča, da jih upravlja po želji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:369
msgid "Journal type determination"
msgstr "Določanje vrste dnevnika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:371
msgid ""
"The journal type is not specified in the format (similar to the accounts) "
"and is initially created with the default type :guilabel:`general`."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta dnevnika ni določena v formatu (podobno kot konti) in je na začetku "
"ustvarjena s privzeto vrsto :guilabel:`splošno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:374
msgid ""
"At the end of the import process, the journal type is determined based on "
"the following rules regarding related moves and accounts:"
msgstr ""
"Ob koncu postopka uvoza se vrsta dnevnika določi na podlagi naslednjih "
"pravil glede povezanih premikov in kontov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`bank`: Moves in these journals always include a line (debit or "
"credit) impacting a liquidity account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`banka`: Premiki v teh dnevnikih vedno vključujejo vrstico (breme "
"ali dobropis), ki vpliva na konto likvidnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`cash` / :guilabel:`bank` can be interchanged, so :guilabel:`bank` "
"is assigned when this condition is met."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`gotovina` / :guilabel:`banka` se lahko zamenjata, zato je "
":guilabel:`banka` dodeljena, ko je ta pogoj izpolnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`sale`: Moves in these journals mostly have debit lines on "
"receivable accounts and credit lines on tax income accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`prodaja`: Prenosi v teh dnevnikih imajo večinoma bremenilne "
"vrstice na kontih terjatev in dobropiše na kontih prihodkov od davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid "Sale refund journal items are debit/credit inverted."
msgstr "Postavke dnevnika dobropisov prodaje so debet/kredit obrnjene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`purchase`: Moves in these journals mostly have credit lines on "
"payable accounts and debit lines on expense accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`nakup`: Prenosi v teh dnevnikih imajo večinoma kreditne vrstice "
"na kontih obveznosti in bremenilne vrstice na kontih odhodkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid "Purchase refund journal items are debit/credit inverted."
msgstr "Postavke dnevnika dobropisov nakupa so debet/kredit obrnjene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`general`: Used for everything else."
msgstr ":guilabel:`splošno`: Uporablja se za vse ostalo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:390
msgid "A minimum of three moves is required to identify the journal type."
msgstr "Za določitev vrste dnevnika so potrebni najmanj trije prenosi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:391
msgid ""
"A threshold of 70% of the moves must meet the criteria for a journal type to "
"be determined."
msgstr ""
"Prag 70 % prenosov mora izpolnjevati merila, da se določi vrsta dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:394
msgid ""
"Suppose we are analyzing the moves that share a "
"certain :guilabel:`journal_id`."
msgstr ""
"Predpostavimo, da analiziramo prenose, ki si delijo določen "
":guilabel:`journal_id`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:397
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:427
msgid "Moves"
msgstr "Premiki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:397
