"Users are responsible for their Odoo system and must operate it carefully. "
"Modifying source code responsible for ensuring data integrity is not allowed."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki so odgovorni za svoj sistem Odoo in ga morajo upravljati "
"previdno. Spreminjanje izvorne kode, odgovorne za zagotavljanje integritete "
"podatkov, ni dovoljeno."

