#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:28
msgid "D.406 declaration"
msgstr "Deklaracija D.406"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:30
msgid ""
"Starting January 1, 2023, companies registered for tax purposes in Romania "
"must report their accounting data to the Romanian Tax Agency monthly or "
"quarterly in the D.406 declaration."
msgstr ""
"Od 1. januarja 2023 morajo podjetja, registrirana za davčne namene v "
"Romuniji, mesečno ali četrtletno poročati svoje računovodske podatke "
"romunski davčni upravi v deklaraciji D.406."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:33
msgid ""
"Odoo provides all you need to export the data of this declaration in the SAF-"
"T XML format, which you can validate and sign using the software provided by "
"the Romanian Tax Agency."
msgstr ""
"Odoo zagotavlja vse, kar potrebujete za izvoz podatkov te deklaracije v "
"formatu SAF-T XML, ki ga lahko preverite in podpišete s programsko opremo "
"romunske davčne uprave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:37
msgid ""
"Currently, Odoo only supports the generation of the monthly/quarterly D.406 "
"declaration (containing journal entries, invoices, vendor bills, and "
"payments). The yearly declaration (including assets) and the on-demand "
"declaration (including inventory) are not yet supported."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno Odoo podpira samo ustvarjanje mesečne/četrtletne deklaracije D.406 "
"(ki vsebuje knjižbe, račune, dobaviteljeve račune in plačila). Letna "
"deklaracija (vključno s sredstvi) in deklaracija na zahtevo (vključno z "
"zalogo) še nista podprti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:47
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Settings --> General Settings`, in the **Companies** "
"section, click :guilabel:`Update Info` and fill in the "
"company's :guilabel:`Country`, :guilabel:`City`, and :guilabel:`Telephone "
"Number`."
msgstr ""
"V :guilabel:`Nastavitve --> Splošne nastavitve`, v razdelku **Podjetja**, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Posodobi podatke` in izpolnite :guilabel:`Državo`, "
":guilabel:`Mesto` in :guilabel:`Telefonsko številko` podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:50
msgid ""
"Provide your company's :abbr:`CUI (Codul Unic de Inregistrare)` number "
"or :abbr:`CIF (*Codul de identificare fiscală*)` number (for foreign "
"companies) in the :guilabel:`Company ID` field, without the `RO` prefix "
"(e.g., `18547290`)."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`ID podjetja` vnesite :abbr:`CUI (Codul Unic de "
"Inregistrare)` številko vašega podjetja ali :abbr:`CIF (Codul de "
"identificare fiscală)` številko (za tuja podjetja) brez predpone `RO` (npr. "
"`18547290`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:53
msgid ""
"If your company is **registered** for VAT in Romania, fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` field number, including the `RO` prefix (e.g., "
"`RO18547290`). If the company is **not** registered for VAT in Romania, you "
"**must not** fill in the :guilabel:`Tax ID` field."
msgstr ""
"Če je vaše podjetje **registrirano** za DDV v Romuniji, izpolnite polje "
":guilabel:`Davčna številka` vključno s predpono `RO` (npr. `RO18547290`). Če "
"podjetje **ni** registrirano za DDV v Romuniji, polja :guilabel:`Davčna "
"številka` **ne smete** izpolniti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:56
msgid ""
"Open the **Contacts** app and search for your company. Open your company's "
"profile, and in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line` "
"and add your **bank account number** if not informed already. Make sure the "
"profile is set as :guilabel:`Company` above the **name**."
msgstr ""
"Odprite aplikacijo **Stiki** in poiščite svoje podjetje. Odprite profil "
"svojega podjetja in v zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` ter dodajte **številko bančnega računa**, če še ni "
"vnesena. Prepričajte se, da je profil nastavljen kot :guilabel:`Podjetje` "
"nad **imenom**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:60
msgid ""
"You must have at least one **contact person** linked to your company in the "
"**Contacts** app. If no **contact person** is linked, create a new one by "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`, set it as :guilabel:`Individual`, and select your "
"company in the :guilabel:`Company name` field."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji **Stiki** morate imeti vsaj eno **kontaktno osebo**, povezano z "
"vašim podjetjem. Če ni povezana nobena **kontaktna oseba**, ustvarite novo "
"tako, da kliknete :guilabel:`Novo`, jo nastavite kot :guilabel:`Posameznik` "
"in v polju :guilabel:`Ime podjetja` izberete svoje podjetje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:67
msgid ""
"To generate a file receivable by the Romanian Tax Agency, the chart of "
"accounts must not deviate from an official chart of accounts, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje datoteke, ki jo lahko sprejme romunska davčna uprava, se "
"kontni načrt ne sme odstopati od uradnega kontnega načrta, kot je:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:70
msgid ""
"the chart of accounts for commercial companies (*PlanConturiBalSocCom*), "
"which is installed by default when creating a company with the Romanian "
"localization or;"
msgstr ""
"kontni načrt za gospodarske družbe (*PlanConturiBalSocCom*), ki je privzeto "
"nameščen pri ustvarjanju podjetja z romunsko lokalizacijo ali;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:72
msgid ""
"the chart of accounts for companies following `IFRS <https://www.ifrs.org/"
">`_ (*PlanConturiIFRS*)."
msgstr ""
"kontni načrt za podjetja, ki sledijo `IFRS <https://www.ifrs.org/>`_ "
"(*PlanConturiIFRS*)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:74
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Settings --> Accounting`, in the **Romanian localization** "
"section, set the :guilabel:`Tax Accounting Basis` to reflect the accounting "
"regulations and Chart of Accounts used by the company."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Nastavitve --> Računovodstvo`, v razdelku **Romanska "
"lokalizacija**, nastavite :guilabel:`Davčna računovodska osnova`, da odraža "
"računovodske predpise in kontni načrt, ki ga uporablja podjetje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:82
msgid "Customer and supplier"
msgstr "Stranka in dobavitelj"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:84
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Country`, :guilabel:`City`, and :guilabel:`Zip Code` "
"of each partner that appears in your invoices, vendor bills, or payments "
"through the **Contacts** app."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite :guilabel:`Država`, :guilabel:`Mesto` in :guilabel:`Poštna "
"številka` vsakega partnerja, ki se pojavi na vaših računih, računih "
"dobaviteljev ali plačilih prek aplikacije **Stiki**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:87
msgid ""
"For partners that are companies, you must fill in the VAT number (including "
"the country  prefix) in the :guilabel:`Tax ID` field. If the partner is a "
"company based in Romania, you may instead fill in the CUI number (without "
"the 'RO' prefix) in the :guilabel:`Company ID` field."
msgstr ""
"Za partnerje, ki so podjetja, morate izpolniti davčno številko (vključno s "
"predpono države) v polju :guilabel:`Davčna številka`. Če je partner podjetje "
"s sedežem v Romuniji, lahko namesto tega izpolnite številko CUI (brez "
"predpone 'RO') v polju :guilabel:`ID podjetja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:94
msgid ""
"You must indicate the :guilabel:`Romanian SAF-T Tax Type` (3-digit number) "
"and :guilabel:`Romanian SAF-T Tax Code` (6-digit number) on each of the "
"taxes you use. This is already done for the taxes that exist by default in "
"Odoo. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Taxes`, select the tax you wish to modify, click the :guilabel:`Advanced "
"Options` tab, and fill in the **tax type** and **tax code** fields."
msgstr ""
"Na vsakem od davkov, ki jih uporabljate, morate navesti :guilabel:`Romanska "
"SAF-T vrsta davka` (3-mestna številka) in :guilabel:`Romanska SAF-T koda "
"davka` (6-mestna številka). To je že storjeno za davke, ki privzeto "
"obstajajo v Odoo. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davki`, izberete davek, "
"ki ga želite spremeniti, kliknete zavihek :guilabel:`Napredne možnosti` in "
"izpolnite polji **vrsta davka** in **koda davka**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:101
msgid ""
"The **tax type** and **tax code** are codes defined by the Romanian Tax "
"Agency for the **D.406 declaration**. These can be found in the Excel "
"spreadsheet published as guidance for completing the declaration, which you "
"can find on the `website of the Romanian Tax Agency <https://www.anaf.ro/"
"anaf/internet/ANAF/despre_anaf/strategii_anaf/proiecte_digitalizare/saf_t/"
">`_."
msgstr ""
"**Vrsta davka** in **koda davka** sta kodi, ki ju je določila Romanska "
"davčna uprava za **napoved D.406**. Te najdete v Excelovi preglednici, "
"objavljeni kot navodilo za izpolnjevanje napovedi, ki jo najdete na `spletni "
"strani Romanske davčne uprave <https://www.anaf.ro/anaf/internet/ANAF/"
"despre_anaf/strategii_anaf/proiecte_digitalizare/saf_t/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:111
msgid ""
"For some types of goods transactions, the :guilabel:`Intrastat Code` (Cod "
"NC) must be configured on the product, as it is required by Romanian law:"
msgstr ""
"Za nekatere vrste transakcij z blagom je treba na izdelku konfigurirati "
":guilabel:`Koda Intrastat` (Cod NC), saj jo zahteva romunska zakonodaja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:114
msgid "import / export transactions;"
msgstr "transakcije uvoza / izvoza;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:115
msgid "acquisitions / supplies of food products subjected to reduced VAT rate;"
msgstr ""
"pridobitve / dobave živilskih izdelkov, ki so predmet nižje stopnje DDV;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:116
msgid "intra-community movements subjected to intrastat reporting;"
msgstr "intrakomunitarni prenosi, ki so predmet poročanja Intrastat;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:117
msgid ""
"acquisitions / supplies subjected to local reversed VAT charge (depending on "
"Cod NC); and"
msgstr ""
"pridobitve / dobave, ki so predmet lokalne obrnjene davčne obremenitve DDV "
"(odvisno od Cod NC); in"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:118
msgid ""
"transactions with excisable products for which excise duties are determined "
"based on the Cod NC."
msgstr ""
"transakcije z akciznimi izdelki, za katere se akcize določajo na podlagi Cod "
"NC."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:120
msgid ""
"If the Intrastat Code is not specified on a non-service product, the default "
"code '0' will be used."
msgstr ""
"Če koda Intrastat ni navedena na izdelku, ki ni storitev, bo uporabljena "
"privzeta koda '0'."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:122
msgid ""
"To configure the :guilabel:`Intrastat Codes`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Products`, select a product, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, set a :guilabel:`Commodity Code`."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo :guilabel:`Kod Intrastat` pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Izdelki`, izberite izdelek in "
"v zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` nastavite :guilabel:`Koda blaga`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:127
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/reporting/intrastat`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/reporting/intrastat`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:132
msgid ""
"You must check the :guilabel:`Is self-invoice (RO)?` checkbox in "
"the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab for any vendor bill that is a self-invoice "
"(i.e. a vendor bill that you issued yourself in the absence of an invoice "
"document received from a supplier)."
msgstr ""
"Za vsak račun dobavitelja, ki je samoizstavljeni račun (tj. račun "
"dobavitelja, ki ste ga izdali sami v odsotnosti računa, prejetega od "
"dobavitelja), morate v zavihku :guilabel:`Druge informacije` označiti "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Je samoizstavljeni račun (RO)?`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:137
msgid "Generating the declaration"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje napovedi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:140
msgid "Exporting your data"
msgstr "Izvoz vaših podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:142
msgid ""
"To export the XML for the D.406 declaration, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reports --> General Ledger` and click "
"on :guilabel:`SAF-T`."
msgstr ""
"Za izvoz XML za napoved D.406 pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročila --> Glavna knjiga` in kliknite :guilabel:`SAF-T`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:None
msgid "Click on the 'SAF-T' button to export the D.406 XML declaration."
msgstr "Kliknite na gumb 'SAF-T' za izvoz deklaracije D.406 XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:149
msgid ""
"You can then validate and sign the XML file using the Romanian Tax Agency's "
"validation software, *DUKIntegrator*."
msgstr ""
"Nato lahko XML datoteko preverite in podpišete s programsko opremo za "
"preverjanje romunske davčne uprave, *DUKIntegrator*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:153
msgid "Signing the report"
msgstr "Podpisovanje poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:155
msgid ""
"Download and install the *DUKIntegrator* validation software found on the "
"`website of the Romanian Tax Agency <https://www.anaf.ro/anaf/internet/ANAF/"
"despre_anaf/strategii_anaf/proiecte_digitalizare/saf_t/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Prenesite in namestite programsko opremo za preverjanje *DUKIntegrator*, ki "
"jo najdete na `spletni strani romunske davčne uprave <https://www.anaf.ro/"
"anaf/internet/ANAF/despre_anaf/strategii_anaf/proiecte_digitalizare/saf_t/>"
"`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:158
msgid ""
"Once you have generated the XML, open 'DUKIntegrator' and select the file "
"you have just generated."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite XML, odprite 'DUKIntegrator' in izberite datoteko, ki ste jo "
"pravkar ustvarili."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:160
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Validare + creare PDF` to create an **unsigned** PDF "
"containing your report, or :guilabel:`Validare + creare PDF semnat` to "
"create a **signed** PDF containing your report."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na :guilabel:`Validare + creare PDF`, da ustvarite **nepodpisan** "
"PDF s svojim poročilom, ali :guilabel:`Validare + creare PDF semnat`, da "
"ustvarite **podpisan** PDF s svojim poročilom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:None
msgid "The DUKIntegrator validation software."
msgstr "Programska oprema za preverjanje DUKIntegrator."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:167
msgid ""
"If the *DUKIntegrator* validator detects errors or inconsistencies in your "
"data, it generates a file that explains the errors. In this case, you need "
"to correct those inconsistencies in your data before you can submit the "
"report to the Romanian Tax Agency."
msgstr ""
"Če validacijska programska oprema *DUKIntegrator* zazna napake ali neskladja "
"v vaših podatkih, ustvari datoteko, ki pojasnjuje napake. V tem primeru "
"morate popraviti ta neskladja v vaših podatkih, preden lahko poročilo "
"predložite romunski davčni upravi."

