#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:160
msgid ""
"Each provider has its own specific configuration flow, depending on which "
"feature is available."
msgstr ""
"Vsak ponudnik ima svoj poseben postopek konfiguracije, odvisno od tega, "
"katera funkcija je na voljo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:162
msgid ""
"Some of these online payment providers can also be added as :doc:`bank "
"accounts <../finance/accounting/bank>`, but this is **not** the same process "
"as adding them as payment providers. Payment providers allow customers to "
"pay online, and bank accounts are added and configured in the Accounting app "
"to do a :doc:`bank reconciliation <accounting/bank/reconciliation>`."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere od teh spletnih ponudnikov plačil je mogoče dodati tudi kot "
":doc:`bančne račune <../finance/accounting/bank>`, vendar to **ni** enak "
"postopek kot dodajanje ponudnikov plačil. Ponudniki plačil strankam "
"omogočajo spletno plačevanje, bančni računi pa se dodajo in konfigurirajo v "
"aplikaciji Računovodstvo za :doc:`bančno uskladitev <accounting/bank/"
"reconciliation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:169
msgid ""
"In addition to the regular payment providers that integrate with an API, "
"such as Stripe, PayPal, or Adyen, Odoo bundles the :doc:`Demo payment "
"provider <payment_providers/demo>`. This payment provider allows you to test "
"business flows involving online payments. No credentials are required as the "
"demo payments are dummy payments."
msgstr ""
"Poleg rednih ponudnikov plačil, ki se integrirajo z API-jem, kot so Stripe, "
"PayPal ali Adyen, Odoo vključuje :doc:`Demo ponudnika plačil "
"<payment_providers/demo>`. Ta ponudnik plačil vam omogoča testiranje "
"poslovnih procesov, ki vključujejo spletna plačila. Poverilnice niso "
"potrebne, saj so demo plačila navidezna plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:177
