":guilabel:`Dynamic eCommerce Parameters` should contain the following "
"values: `ALIAS`, `AMOUNT`, `CARDNO`, `CN`, `CURRENCY`, `IP`, `NCERROR` "
"`ORDERID`, `PAYID`, `PM`, `STATUS`, `TRXDATE`. Other parameters can be "
